nt%E2%80%99s%20genius%20lay%20in%20its%20realism%20and%20complex%20themes.%20The%20filmmakers%20during%20this%20time%20brought%20style%20and%20substance%20to%20the%20rhetoric%2C%20allowing%20societal%20issues%20to%20be%20viewed%20from%20a%20nuanced%20lens.%20But%20in%20the%20decades%20that%20followed%2C%20this%20cinematic%20brilliance%20was%20wrestled%20from%20the%20city%20by%20commercial%20mainstream%20movies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMumbai%E2%80%99s%20seams%20began%20bursting%20with%20urban%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20puts%20the%20case%20into%20point%20as%20she%20speaks%20of%20how%20this%20increased%20the%20pressure%20on%20art%20and%20artists.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20evolution%20of%20Bombay%2C%20art%20became%20a%20victim.%20And%2C%20in%20the%20battle%20between%20commerce%20and%20art%2C%20we%20gave%20in%20to%20commerce.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20art%20scene%20found%20shelter%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdespair%20and%20urgency%E2%80%9D%20she%20felt%20at%20wanting%20to%20revive%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20imaginative%20palette%20once%20again%2C%20before%20contemporary%20art%20became%20an%20enigma%2C%20Parikh%20says%20she%20needed%20a%20space%20to%20let%20her%20plans%20unfold.%20The%20dots%20connected%20and%20led%20her%20to%20the%20warehouse%2C%20which%20stood%20desolate%20on%20the%20piece%20of%20land%20where%20her%20father%20earlier%20ran%20his%20printing%20press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20thought%20was%20to%20create%20a%20space%20whose%20doors%20would%20be%20open%20to%20everyone.%20A%20space%20that%20would%20feel%20welcoming%20and%20like%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20shares.