ier%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20which%20prohibits%20child%20labour%20and%20insists%20on%20low-waste%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHandmade%20with%20love%3A%20Inside%20the%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormulations%20are%20developed%20and%20tested%20in%20a%20small%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20within%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20office%20on%20Bowring%20Hospital%20Road%2C%20which%20also%20houses%20the%20production%20unit%20and%20warehouse.%20The%20products%2C%20especially%20their%20soaps%2C%20are%20handmade%20using%20the%20cold-process%20saponification%20method%2C%20blending%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F392137%2Fheart-in-hills-foreka-cold-pressed-oil-driving-rural-economic-growth-through-fair-trade-and-sustainability-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20sunflower%20or%20coconut%20oil%20with%20natural%20clays%20such%20as%20green%20and%20pink%20clay%2C%20and%20essential%20oils%20for%20fragrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20is%20clear%20about%20her%20intentions.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCG)%20industry%20focuses%20on%20cheap%20and%20plastic-laden%20products%20filled%20with%20microplastics%20and%20water.%20We%20want%20to%20show%20that%20effective%2C%20luxurious%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20come%20at%20the%20planet%E2%80%99s%20expense%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20made%20an%20impressive%20environmental%20dent.%20Since%20their%20inception%20in%202016%2C%20Bare%20Necessities%20has%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESold%20over%20241%2C805%20products%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESaved%20more%20than%2068.8%20million%20units%20of%20single-use%20plastic%20from%20entering%20the%20environment%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiverted%20over%20155%2C816%20kilograms%20of%20waste%20from%20landfills%20and%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Formulations%20of%20the%20products%20are%20developed%20and%20tested%20in%20a%20small%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20within%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20office%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-436563%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFormulations%20of%20the%20products%20are%20developed%20and%20tested%20in%20a%20small%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20within%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20office%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20impact%20is%20measured%20in%20line%20